title: Ask HN: Would this idea work? Audiobook visualizer
text:
Product idea: Audiobook visualizer

1. Use DallE/Midjourney/Stable Diffusion to create animated movies from a book transcription.

I imagine there will have to be a human who filters some of this.

2. Use ffmpeg to create waveforms and overlay them on the movie.

Listen to a good book in front of the fireplace.
